name: Brian'sFriend
0:
”Alexa, open Brian's Friend.”
”I'd like a workout.”
”I want to tell you a joke.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: brian's friend
des:
This skill will listen to your jokes and react accordingly. It cannot give you any jokes though. 

If you're not working on a standup comedy routine, but would like to get some exercise, ask Brian's Friend for a workout! Get a random workout based on whether you want to be indoors or outdoors. There are no additional hardware or account requirements to use this skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
